'''紫色色桿菌'''（''Chromobacterium violaceum''）是一種[[革蘭氏陰性菌|革蘭氏陰性]]、兼性厭氧及無芽孢的[[球桿菌|球桿菌]]。在[[熱帶|熱帶]]及[[亞熱帶|亞熱帶]]的水中及[[土壤|土壤]][[植物|植物]]可以找到。它們會生產出紫色桿菌素。它們可以在營養瓊脂中生長，並形成平滑及低突起的菌落，帶有金屬暗紫色的光澤。它們的完整[[基因組|基因組]]已於2003年被公布。<ref>{{cite journal en| journal=Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A | volume=100 | pages=11660-11665 | year=2003 | author=Brazilian National Genome Project Consortium. | title=The complete genome sequence of Chromobacterium violaceum reveals remarkable and exploitable bacterial adaptability. | id=PMID 14500782}}</ref>

==生物化學==
紫色色桿菌發酵[[葡萄糖|葡萄糖]]、[[海藻糖|海藻糖]]、[[N-乙醯葡萄醣胺|N-乙醯葡萄醣胺]]及[[葡萄糖酸|葡萄糖酸]]，但卻不能發酵L-[[阿拉伯糖|阿拉伯糖]]、D-[[半乳糖|半乳糖]]或D-[[麥芽糖|麥芽糖]]。

==醫藥特性==
紫色色桿菌很少會感染[[人類|人類]]，但若發生感染，則會引起[[皮膚|皮膚]]損傷、[[敗血症|敗血症]]及可以引致[[死亡|死亡]]的[[肝膿腫|肝膿腫]]。<ref>{{cite journal en | journal=Lancet | year=1953 | volume=265 | issue=6780 | pages=276-277 | title=Fatal infection by ''Chromobacterium violaceum'' | author=Sneath PH, Whelan JP, Bhagwan Singh R, Edwards D. | id=PMID 13085740 }}</ref>很多普遍的方法都會錯將[[類鼻疽伯克氏菌|類鼻疽伯克氏菌]]看為紫色色桿菌。<ref>{{cite journal en | author=Inglis TJ, Chiang D, Lee GS, Chor-Kiang L | title=Potential misidentification of ''Burkholderia pseudomallei'' by API 20NE | year=1998 | journal=Pathology | volume=30 | issue=1 | pages=62-64 | id=PMID: 9534210 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en | author=Lowe P, Engler C, Norton R. | title=Comparison of automated and nonautomated systems for identification of ''Burkholderia pseudomallei'' | url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-clinical-microbiology_2002-12_40_12/page/4625 | journal=J Clin Microbiol | year=2002 | pages=4625-4627 | volume=40 | issue=12 | DOI=10.1128/JCM.40.12.4625-4627.2002 }}</ref>這兩類菌的最大分別是類鼻疽伯克氏菌會產生大量的皺曲菌落。

紫色色桿菌會天然生產一些[[抗生素|抗生素]]：
* [[氨曲南|氨曲南]]是一種單環類抗生素，能有效抵抗好氧的[[革蘭氏陰性菌|革蘭氏陰性菌]]，如[[綠膿桿菌|綠膿桿菌]]。
* 紫色桿菌素能有效抵抗[[變形蟲|變形蟲]]及[[錐蟲|錐蟲]]。
* Aerocyanidine可以抵抗[[革蘭氏陽性菌|革蘭氏陽性菌]]。
* Aerocavin可以抵抗革蘭氏陽性及革蘭氏陰性菌。

==治療==
{{medical}}
由於被紫色色桿菌感染的個案很小，故並未有就不同治療的臨床測試。能有效治療紫色色桿菌感染的[[抗生素|抗生素]]有[[培氟沙星|培氟沙星]]<ref>{{cite journal en | journal=J Clin Microbiol | year=1999 | pages=2068-2070 | volume=37 | issue=6 | author=Lee J, Kim JS, Nahm CH,''et al.'' | title=Two cases of ''Chromobacterium violaceum'' infection after injury in a subtropical region | url=http://jcm.asm.org/cgi/content/full/37/6/2068 | access-date=2008-04-21 | archive-date=2011-09-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927141825/http://jcm.asm.org/cgi/content/full/37/6/2068 | dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[環丙沙星|環丙沙星]]、[[阿米卡星|阿米卡星]]<ref>{{cite journal en| author=Ray P, Sharma J, Marak RSK, ''et al.'' | title=''Chromobacterium violaceum'' septicaemia from north India | journal=Indian J Med Res | volume=120 | year=2004 | pages=523-526 }}</ref>及[[磺胺甲基異惡唑|磺胺甲基異惡唑]]。<ref>{{cite journal en | author = Moore C, Lane J, Stephens J | title = Successful treatment of an infant with ''Chromobacterium violaceum'' sepsis. | journal = Clin Infect Dis | volume = 32 | issue = 6 | pages = E107-110 | year = 2001 | id = PMID 11247733}}</ref>其他有效的[[靜脈|靜脈]]注射抗生素有[[氯黴素|氯黴素]]及[[四環黴素|四環黴素]]。<ref>{{cite journal en | journal=Rev Inst Med Trop Sao Paulo | year=2000 | volume=42 | issue=2 | pages=111-113 | title=''Chromobacterium violaceum'' infection in Brazil. A case report | author=Martinez R, Velludo MA, Santos VR, Dinamarco PV. }}</ref>理論上，紫色色桿菌感染對[[青黴素|青黴素]]、[[頭孢菌素|頭孢菌素]]或[[氨曲南|氨曲南]]沒有反應，不過當中一些[[碳青黴烯|碳青黴烯]]如[[美羅培南|美羅培南]]或[[亞安培南|亞安培南]]則可能有效。<ref>{{cite journal en | author = Midani S, Rathore M | title = Chromobacterium violaceum infection. | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_southern-medical-journal_1998-05_91_5/page/464 | journal = South Med J | volume = 91 | issue = 5 | pages = 464-466 | year = 1998 | id = PMID 9598856}}</ref>

